          %p
            Decision Data Resources specializes in providing Software as Service solutions through their web-based data and Geographic Information System (GIS) applications.  DDR's IE360 is the only web-based GIS solution offering direct access to decision critical innovation data including Venture Capital, Patents and Federal Funding. IE360 also includes county level Industry Output and Employment/Wage data and also provides Data Visualization tools for creating chart and graph outputs and targeted industry cluster analysis. The isotope|eleven team worked closely with the DDR team to conceptualize, design, build and launch this innovative and robust service.
